{"tid":1746800,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"機場紅隧中環通通都唔係春袋","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:21:30.000Z","uid":205884,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5406fb92a539f2ca1313ea1c592113d762b6b88","tid":1746800,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"真正春袋只有一個<br />\n就係中美貿易戰個Deal<br />\n<br />\n香港人係時候要認清<br />\n我地真正既對家根本唔係特區政府或者警隊<br />\n佢地只係共產黨既扯線公仔<br />\n五大訴求可唔可以得到<br />\n係阿平仔一念之差<br />\n而你要知道佢care啲乜<br />\n<br />\n好坦白講<br />\n呢條友係顛鳩黎<br />\n就算全香港陷入一片火海<br />\n都係唔會讓步架<br />\n但依家佢care個 trade deal<br />\n因為trade deal平仔唔敢出兵<br />\n<br />\n面對大你咁多既大國<br />\n你唯一勝算只有另一個大國<br />\n而依家人類最強國家係企我地呢邊<br />\n只要香港人仍然堅持普世價值美國係唔會比我地衰<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要做有針對性既野<br />\n做多啲可以令國際社會同情既野<br />\n香港人，搵食姐<br />\n阻人搵食真係百害而無一利"},{"pid":"7e0045dc411deec7234cee9bbd64436098a30a92","tid":1746800,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc829b14b17ca5cff0b0f3cbdb1f563e7a556c3","tid":1746800,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你好我係拍片嘅本人，有冇人知道個手足點樣？可以幫手retweet 比多啲人睇到,想推到出國際俾記者報道同有冇人知道有咩方法可以 ？謝謝 Twitter link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hker_ng/status/1196632031314137094?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhker_ng%2Fstatus%2F1196632031314137094%3Fs%3D21&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=d6f4879f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhker_ng%2Fstatus%2F1196632031314137094%3Fs%3D21&h=e7bf2029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hker_ng/status/1196632031314137094?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTub